wikipedia_page.main: Michael McNeil (born 7 February 1940) is a former Middlesbrough and Ipswich Town footballer who made nine appearances for England in 1960 and 1961. During his career he made 178 Football League appearances for Middlesbrough and almost 150 appearances for Ipswich Town.
